text:
It is a nice bridge allowing pedestrians safely passing between two sides of the crowded road.

The bridge is planted with a decent amount of bougainvillea, nice landscaping. There are also plenty of shaded seats around to rest and enjoy the view, take rest and cool down during hot days.
Mini garden bridge.  Nice place for short stop to relax from a long walk of shopping at Chinatown.
I love this place. On weekends you can see the uncles singing :)
